import os

from streams.generators.__init__ import *

stream_name = "led"

project_path = "new dataset/" + stream_name + "/"
if not os.path.exists(project_path):
    os.makedirs(project_path)

file_path = project_path + stream_name

stream_generator = LEDConceptDrift(concept_length=25000)
stream_generator.generate(file_path)

You are going to generate a LEDConceptDrift data stream containing 100000 instances, and 3 concept drifts; 
where they appear at every 25000 instances.
You can find the generated files in new dataset/led/led.arff!
